      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Yes, I used the foundry cell library for my TT design and it had this issue. I wrote a quick librelane plugin to fix it that’s linked from here https://github.com/librelane/librelane/issues/967\nyou can see how I injected it into the config here: https://github.com/MichaelBell/ttgf0p3-tinyQV/blob/c02a42568e2f9dcf6b6ba6f78fe7b5f818b97e76/src/config.json#L73 (will need converting to yaml)\nAnd then I think you just need that plugin on the PYTHONPATH and it should work",
      "author": {
        "id": "691780627338625077",
        "name": "rebelmike",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "RebelMike",
